🎯 Objective: Collect, preserve, and analyze digital evidence from compromised systems.


🧰 Core Tools

• FTK Imager – Disk & memory imaging
• Autopsy – GUI forensic analysis
• Volatility / Volatility 3 – Memory analysis
• KAPE – Rapid triage collection
• Scalpel – File carving
• Windows File Analyzer / JumpList Explorer / PECmd – Windows artifact tools
• Browser History Viewer – Web activity review
• Linux CLI – dd, grep, find, file, stat


